Package field

Class Property

  • java.lang.Object
    • field.FieldElement
      • field.Property
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Domain, PublicService, TrainStation
    public abstract class Property
extends FieldElement
    This class is the base class for every buyable field element. A buyable element is represented by a field element that has an owner and a buying price. A buyable element is also mortgageable so in case of debt, the owner of the property can sell this property to the bank and still possess the property but without receiving its rent.
